## Relay-A5 Cross-View Event Router Architecture
**Status:** approved
**Tags:** stack:frontend

```mermaid
graph TB
    SSE[Server-Sent Events] -->|raw events| ER[useEventRouter.ts]
    ER -->|run_started| R[RelayView]
    ER -->|gate_reached| GI[useGateInbox.ts]
    ER -->|spec_written| S[SpecsView]
    ER -->|run_completed| C[ChatsView ReportCard]
    GI -->|active gate| SM[SecretaryMessage.vue]
    GI -->|badge count| NR[NavRail]
```

- Event router is a singleton that subscribes to `/api/forge/relay/runs/{id}/events`
- It maps event types to view actions without tight coupling
- Gate inbox maintains a queue so multiple gates don't overwhelm the user

